org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network

Class DeviceNameManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network.WifiStartStoppable
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network.DeviceNameManager

  • public class DeviceNameManager
extends WifiStartStoppable
    DeviceNameManager manages the name by which the current device (robot controller or driver station) is known externally. By default, it tracks the WifiDirect name of the device.
